---
(command (word "wc") (word "-l") (redirect "<" "input.txt"))
---


=== sort from file
sort < unsorted.txt
---
(command (word "sort") (redirect "<" "unsorted.txt"))
---


# === File descriptor redirects ===

=== stderr redirect
