---
(command (word "cmd") (redirect ">" "errors.txt"))
---


=== stderr append
cmd 2>> errors.txt
---
(command (word "cmd") (redirect ">>" "errors.txt"))
---


=== stderr to dev null
cmd 2> /dev/null
---
(command (word "cmd") (redirect ">" "/dev/null"))
---


=== stdout and stderr separate
cmd > out.txt 2> err.txt
---
(command (word "cmd") (redirect ">" "out.txt") (redirect ">" "err.txt"))
---


=== fd3 redirect
