(command (word "cat") (redirect "<<<" "'hello world'"))
---


=== here string bare word
cat <<< hello
---
(command (word "cat") (redirect "<<<" "hello"))
---


=== here string with fd
cat 0<<< "hello"
---
(command (word "cat") (redirect "<<<" ""hello""))
